reviews.content: Dr Dieguez is a great doctor and takes the time to speak with you and get to know you.  . He has been very good to my family and I am so appreciative of this.  He cares about his patients and provides the best medical care, very knowledgeable.. His staff is awesome!  I love each of them!  Hard workers and very efficient!

This doctor is the best and really listens do you and takes care of you like a family member,  the staff is excellent the office location is excellent ,on State Road 200 , accessible from anywhere in Ocala and citrus county.. The doctor is very human and also has a nurse practitioner on staff that is excellent
